;"> fun facts</span><span style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);"> about themselves, their favourite K-Beauty products, and what makes them proud to be a part of this phenomenal team. So sit back, relax, and get ready to bask in the glow of some truly fabulous women!</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1654068384382" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1654068384382"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1654068600900" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1654068600900" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1654067669120" data-id="1654067669120"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1678111697751" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1678111697751" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/dc4002f7-d435-46c4-bf33-582c30c3015c/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Monica---Pink.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="50%" data-height="auto" title="" width="800" height="800" natural-width="800" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1654068600862" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1654068600862" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 28px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 14px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-center-md" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-104717" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Monica</h2></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1677750617498" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1677750617498" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 44px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 22px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 53px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-center-md" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-419339" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></h2><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Founder</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1654068600939" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1654068600939"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 793.906px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 396.953px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 793.906px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="385" height="664" style="display: none; top: 104px !important; left: 287px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-855569" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><span style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);">Hello and welcome, I'm Monica!</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><strong style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);">What sparked your interest in Korean skin care?</strong></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><span style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);">From a young age I was curious and interested in Korean culture and skin care. This stems from when I was introduced to the captivating world of <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">K-dramas</span> by a dear friend. I was hooked from the moment I watched 'You're Beautiful' and was completely enthralled with the emotional journey each drama took me on. I even got my dad addicted to K-dramas, and my mom joked that I should stop recommending shows because it was causing late-night binges in our house!</span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><span style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);"><br></span></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><font color="#3d4246"><span style="caret-color: rgb(61, 66, 70);"><b>What made you start a Korean skin care company?</b></span></font></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><span style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);">I am originally from the United States, and moved to The Netherlands with my Belgian husband. When my husband would travel for work, he would bring me <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">skin care as gifts </span></span><span style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70);">&nbsp;from Korea. This was super special to me, because as most expats know, it can be lonely moving to a new country.</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">The gift of skin care allowed me to have that <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">self-love moment</span>. After a few years of traveling to Korea, there was this thought of “Is there a market in Europe for Korean skin care products?” I was happy to find out there is, and so after only a few months postpartum KS was born.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">What do you like most about KS?</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">I cannot express how much KS means to me. I <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">appreciate</span> all the kind messages we receive. Likewise, I also love being able to <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">help with skin concerns</span>, and getting to know our customers more. I have made some <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">lifelong friends</span> through the love of Korean skin care products, and I am extremely <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">grateful</span> to the talented staff members that have chosen to be part of this team.&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><span style="font-weight: 700;">What do you like to do in your free time?&nbsp;</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">I enjoy watching Korean drama’s and reading a ton of Webtoons. I am a big fan of collecting fun mugs and like eating anything that is mint chocolate chip. I love spending time with my family, but also enjoy taking a nice bubble bath.&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><b>Monica's favourite products:</b></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1678111639935" data-id="1678111639935"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1677751305138" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1677751305138" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/b5fc7ee9-46aa-45b8-8177-c21840867449/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Monica---Pink.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="75%" data-height="auto" title="" width="800" height="800" natural-width="800" natural-height="800"></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Carousel" data-key="carousel" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1678111308254" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-carousel" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1678111308254"><div class="module main-slider owl-carousel owl-theme " data-collg="3" data-colmd="3" data-colsm="3" data-colxs="1" data-marginlg="0px" data-marginmd="5px" data-marginsm="5px" data-marginxs="5px" data-dotslg="1" data-dotsmd="1" data-dotssm="1"