m="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></h2><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Marketing Team</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1677751000333" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1677751000333"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 644.844px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 322.422px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 644.844px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="14" height="20" style="display: none; top: 622px !important; left: 284px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-38138" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">Hi there! My name is Merve, and if you’ve read the SkinTalks blog before, you might remember me from the '<span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">3 Make-Up Looks For Valentine’s Day</span>' blog.</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Tell us about your passion!</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">I am passionate about<span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);"> marketing</span>, which is why I am happy to be a part of the Korean Skincare’s marketing team. From social media campaigns to e-mail campaigns, I enjoy learning about the <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">latest trends</span> and applying them to create a deeper connection. My favorite part of working at KS is making this connection with not only my coworkers but also all Korean Skincare members.&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">What do you do in your spare time?</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">You can find me stretching on my yoga mat or meditating in my free time. I love spending time in art museums. When I feel inspired, I sometimes take the brushes and <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">get disconnected</span> from the world while painting. The same thing happens while I listen to techno music.</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, 