="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1654069022131" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 22px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 11px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-center-md" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-322854" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Lori</h2></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1677750597215" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1677750597215" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 44px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 22px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 53px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-419339" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></h2><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Content Team</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1654069222694" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1654069222694"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 765.328px !important; height: 644.844px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 382.664px 322.422px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 765px !important; height: 644.844px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="14" height="20" style="display: none; top: 622px !important; left: 284px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-justify-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-38138" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">Hi all, my name is Lori, and I’m the newest member of the KS team.&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><strong>Who is Lori?</strong></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">Me in a nutshell? Energetic, creative and a real <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">TikTok addict</span>. I might be short, but I’m never short of energy! That’s why I just drink coffee for the aesthetics (and taste!). One second I’m running around with my notebook to brainstorm on new ideas and the other second I’m filming a new TikTok video, and always thinking about the next trending thing might be. I am very dedicated to bringing you the best content!</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">I’m currently really into self-care: from skincare to incorporating <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">new healthy habits</span> into my life. But it’s not all about that, having fun is also key! From going to festivals, following dance classes and making good memories with friends.&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><strong>Tell us about your obsessions!</strong></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">My current <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">obsession</span> is creating new aesthetic Spotify playlists and Pinterest boards. I can literally do that all day and just enjoy being a creative girly. Talking about obsessions: dogs! Don’t walk around the city with me, because I NEED to pet every dog that passes by. But also animals in general is my thing *watches 2 hours of animal videos straight*.&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">I love cooking and trying new recipes. My food might not always look picture-perfect, but it always tastes good - and hey, that’s the most important thing right?&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;">You can talk beauty to me all day, and in specific: Korean skin care. I’m obsessed with the <span style="background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">everlasting glow</span> these products give and I just can’t get enough! That’s why I’m so excited to be part of this beauty team: hello dream job!</p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Lori's favourite products:</span></p><p style="color: rgb(61, 66, 70); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important;"><br></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_co